<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>١٥٠٥ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5178">قَبِيصَةُ: </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2472">سُفْيَانُ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2175">زَيْدِ بْنِ أَسْلَمَ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4975">عِيَاضِ بْنِ عَبْدِ اللهِ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2313">أَبِي سَعِيدٍ </a><span class="special">﵁</span> قَالَ: <span class="c2">«كُنَّا نُطْعِمُ الصَّدَقَةَ صَاعًا مِنْ شَعِيرٍ.»</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>